speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Wow. Thank you. What a crowd. What a beautiful crowd. Look at that, you can’t even see the end of it. What a great crowd. Thank you very much. Hello, Wisconsin. We’re back. We’re back. We’re going to win. We’re going to win this state. We win this state, you know what? It’s over, if we win Wisconsin. I’ve treated Wisconsin very well. Four days from now, we’re going to win this state and we’re going to win four more beautiful years in the White House. With your support, we will continue to bring back your jobs, cut your taxes, cut regulations, support our great police, defend our borders. Without borders, we don’t have a country, do we?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Protect our second amendment, protect religious liberty and ensure more products are proudly stamped with those beautiful words, “Made in the USA.” They’re starting to do that. You remember, I used to say four years ago, “We’re going to bring back the words Merry Christmas.” We did, right? Merry Christmas. Those big department stores, they liked happy New Year. I said, “No, you can say them both, but you can’t do one without the other.” Merry Christmas is back. You notice that right? And pretty soon we’re going to be there. Joe Biden will shut down your state’s economy, wipe out your factories, ship your jobs to China.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Crowd
transcription: Boo.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: To China, that’s paid him off by the way. China that’s paid him off. You know that, right? Although you don’t get too much news, but you get enough, you know what’s going on. They don’t like giving you the news. Punish your family with a $4 trillion tax hike, eliminate private healthcare. 180 million people have private health care, they want to take it away. And send your state into a catastrophic… Do you want to use the word recession or depression? Because the word is depression. Biden has vowed to eliminate the entire US oil industry, no fracking, no energy and gas prices going five, six, $7 for a gallon. How do you like $2 gasoline, good? There’ll be no heating in the winter, no air conditioning in the summer and no electricity whenever the hell you want it. Right now, you have it made. You’re so lucky. You are so lucky I’m your president. And your team is doing a good job, right? They’re doing a good job, right? They are doing a good job. And while I’m president, America will proudly remain energy independent. How does that sound? First time, you’re energy independent. We’re the biggest in the world, nobody close. Biden will deliver poverty, misery, depression. I will deliver jobs, jobs, jobs, and the greatest economy in the history of our country. That’s going to be next year, you see it. Yesterday it was announced, last quarter, our economy grew at the astonishing speed, 33.1%. The largest GDP growth ever recorded. And not just by a little bit, by more than double. Right? And that was in 1952, but more than double. Think of it. It’s never been anything like that, for any country. Not only ours, for any country. In the past five months, we’ve created a record 11.4 million American jobs. We have a super V. I used to talk about the V. This is no longer V, this is a super V. This is despite the fact that the Democrat governors have States shut down, right? Gee, does that sound-
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Crowd
transcription: Boo.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Hey, does that sound familiar to you? Middle-class family income is up more than $6,000 under my administration, far greater than the past administration. I mean, that was not up. That was doing very poorly. We created the greatest economy in history, and now we’re doing it again. Make America Great Again, again. We did it once. That hat, see that hat is now obsolete. It’s called Make America Great Again, again. In a very recent poll Gallup, they said 56% of Americans said they were doing better today than they were four years ago. And we’re rounding the turn on a pandemic and it’s 56. And it’s the highest number they’ve ever recorded, so we’re doing something right.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Joe Biden has spent the last 47 years outsourcing your jobs, opening your borders and sacrificing American blood and treasure in endless foreign wars, in countries that most of you have never even heard of. I mean, think of it. And you know, at the debate… Did anybody see the debate by any chance? During the debate, he’d say, “Well, we’re going to do this.” I said, “Joe, why didn’t you do it?” “We’re going to do that. We’re going to do this to that, this and that.” “Joe, why didn’t you do it, Joe?” That was an easy debate. 91% to 9%, they said. That was good. That’s like a great football game. No, I said, “But Joe…” I said, “Joe, why didn’t you do it?” “Well, I don’t know exactly.” And then the last question was a disaster. Basically, he said, no more oil, no more fracking, no more anything. I said, “Did he say that?”
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: And I just said, “We just left a great place…” You know that. It was a little cold there. This is like warm by comparison. This is a pleasure. This is a pleasure. That was cold. I said, “Let’s cut this a little bit shorter,” but we have a big crowd. We had a big crowd. No matter where we go, we have these massive crowds And I’m going up to Minnesota. We’re going to Minnesota, which we have a chance. Not since 1972, think of it. So those are odds that aren’t good, but they like us up there, with the Iron Range, all the things I’ve done for them up there. And helping them when the rioters and anarchist attacked. We took over and we did a great job. But they should have called us two weeks earlier, in all fairness, and they called. If they called us, federal government, if they called us two weeks earlier, that would have been nice. You would have had no problem. It took us about what? 25 minutes to solve the problem, right? Boom, they just marched.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: But we’re going and governor just informed us though, that… So we have 25,000 people, 25,000 people, that’s lot. You got a lot here. 25,000 people in Minnesota. They said we can only have 250 people. So they were hoping I’d say, “Oh, well, we can’t do that. Let’s turn around.” No, we’re going to go. We’re going to go. It’ll be a very interesting trip. Even if we see 250 people… Can I be honest with you? Everybody understands, you can’t play those games. That could very well, aside from Omar… Omar’s our secret weapon. Ilhan Omar, that’s our secret weapon in Minnesota. No, she doesn’t love our country. I don’t like people that don’t love our country, I don’t. And the other, and you know all about this because you’ve had your things, the other is we want law and order. We’ve got to have law and order. You look at what’s going on in Philadelphia, we can’t have that. You have to let the police do what they do. I mean, they have to do their job.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: When I watched that, again Democrats, it’s all Democrats, when I watched that and people are looting stores and you have the anarchists, the rioters, but they’re looting stores. They’re walking out with dishwashers. They’re walking out, guy has a dishwasher, he couldn’t even… He’s pushing it. Their washer… I mean, they have television sets and they’re walking and the police are standing there. And those police don’t want to be standing there. They don’t want to do that. They want to be able to do their job, but they’re not. And you can’t have that. We need law and order, as we had right here, as we did a very good job right here. We got the endorsement of everybody. Everybody in your state, every law enforcement group in your state endorsed us. I think every law enforcement group in the country endorsed us.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: I asked sleepy Joe, during one of the debates, I said, “Joe, who endorsed you from law enforcement?” And he couldn’t answer the question. Now possibly that happened, but he’s got a very bad memory too. He can’t… He was going, “Now, let me think. Give me about 20 minutes, I’ll figure it out.” I doubt he has any. I doubt he has any. I think we have everybody. We have everybody, Florida, Texas, Oklahoma. Chicago endorsed us. Isn’t that nice? Chicago, with all the problems they have. And they have a great group of people from law enforcement. They could stop those problems. I mean, you see what’s going on there. New York has gone through the roof, New York’s finest. We have New York’s finest, these are incredible police. They could do the job, but they have to be allowed to do the job. And they endorsed me. First time in the history of the police force in New York, that they endorsed a presidential candidate, so it was pretty cool.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: So Joe Biden tried to cut Medicare, during the course of his terms and he worked very hard on cutting social. You wouldn’t believe that, right? And we actually put it up. We put it on… Where is that screen? For places that we really like, we use the screen. It’s very expensive. You’ll see. Biden was a cheerleader for NAFTA, which is the worst trade deal ever made and China’s entry into the World Trade Organization. Which of course Wisconsin, 130 minimum manufacturing jobs. At every turn, Biden betrayed American workers and twisted his knife into the back of Wisconsin workers. You suffered as much as anybody. Biden’s also spent half a century, really a half a century, betraying Black Americans. He devastated Black families with the 1994 Crime Bill. And he called Black youth, “Super predators,” a term that’s a terrible term. Super predators over and over again. And then he wonders why they’re not doing well with the Black vote. The Black votes not turning out for him.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: See, now we don’t have to go by the fake polls. Now you see what’s happening. He’s not doing well with the Black vote. You know why? Because they remember that, and they remember 1994 and they remember him calling everybody a super predator. And that’s a term that they don’t like. That’s a term that nobody would like. But they’re not showing up to vote, and others aren’t either. We’re doing great in Florida. We’re doing great in Ohio. We’re doing great in… North Carolina was fantastic. I think we’re doing really good in Pennsylvania. We’re doing very good in Pennsylvania. I think we’re doing good all over the place, you want to know the truth. I think we’re doing good all over. We’re doing great here. I think they just said here we’re either tied or one up or tied or one down.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: It’s like essentially tied. I don’t know how the hell I can be tied with this guy. He’s shot. He’s shot. They said, “Sir, you’re tied in Wisconsin.” Normally that means because we have like a hidden voter, people that don’t want to talk about it, they just go out and vote for Trump. I never knew. Should I be complimented by that? “We don’t want to talk about it. Leave us alone. We’re voting for Trump.” Right? So when you tied, that’s a good thing. But they said, “Sir, we’re tied.” And I said, “That’s interesting.” And then the fake Washington post, ABC, right? Did you see that?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Crowd
transcription: Boo.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: So, we are tied. I was up here two days ago. We gave a great speech. That was a cold one. We gave a speech on a racetrack. We got a lot of people and it was freezing, but I got through that. There was no way that I leave early or the great people of Wisconsin, because you don’t know about that. There was no way. Anyway, this pole, so we’re tied. Let’s say we’re tied, one up, one down, we’re right, boom. Very close, I think we’re going to take it, easily actually. I think we’re going to take it… Because we’re going to have a turnout, probably on Tuesday. Our people like to vote, they like to vote on Tuesday, not even on Sunday or Monday, but [inaudible 00:14:56]. So Washington Post and ABC, it’s called Washington Post-ABC Poll, they come out 17 down. “Donald Trump is 17 down in Wisconsin.”
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Crowd
transcription: Boo.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: I said, Wait a minute, I just left a crowd of 25,000 people or more. They were going crazy. That wasn’t a second place crowd.” We know second place crowds. That was not a second place crowd. And they did it to me four years ago with crooked Hillary. They had me, “He’s down 12,” two weeks to go. You remember? Washington Post-ABC, crooked as hell. It’s called suppression polls. You know what it does? It suppresses the vote. You get depressed. You like Trump. You know, “I like the president, but let’s…” And in the case four years ago, “I like Donald Trump. He’s going to do a good job.”
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: We did more than we said we were going to do. We did more than any administration has ever done in the first three and a half years. But it’s a suppression thing. So when it came out 12 down, we actually wrote them legal letters and everything and then they changed the vote. Can you believe it? They change it, where we were one down, but that was the day before the election. Two weeks to go, 12 down. But this one was 17 down in your state and I said, “I could be three down. I could also be three up.”
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Crowd
transcription: Four more years. Four more years. Four more years. Four more years. Four more years. Four more years.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: I could be three down. I could be four down. I could also be three up or four up. One thing I know, I’m not 17 down. So I called up the best pollster, a guy, it doesn’t matter, let’s just call him John. His first name’s John. I said, “John, can I ask you a question? I just left Wisconsin. We had a tremendous crowd. It was like a love fest. And then I wake up…” True. “And then I wake up like two days later and I see a poll, Washington Post, it’s all over the place…” They love it, all the fake news. Look at all of them back, they’re fake.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Crowd
transcription: Boo.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Among the most dishonest people in the world. Now they have a new thing, they don’t report. They don’t report on criminality, like with the Biden crime family. They don’t want to report. But fortunately, we have guys like Ron Johnson that are willing to say it like it is. It’s true. It’s actually very true, what I just said. He’s fantastic, but we’ll get to him later. Your senator is fantastic. So you take a look and I said, “I’m not 17 now.” And he’s a really smart guy, he says, “No, you’re not.” I said, “But don’t they have to pay a price, like they did it 12 down, four years ago.” And then I said, “Isn’t it a bad thing?” He said, “Yeah, but they want you to lose.” I said, “Well, why don’t they make it that I’m three or two down, or make it believable?” “No, no. Three down or two down’s no good. Because if they go three down, two down, four, even five…” I said, “Make it five.” He said, “No, no good. Because that means you have a chance, that might even bring people out.” They want to…
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: … Because that means you have a chance. That might even bring people out. They want to make it so bad. And they said, “No.” They’re very smart people. They’re very vicious people. And they purposely make these polls phony. They’re phony polls. And he said, “The only way they really can do it, they have to make it so that the people here think you’re 17 down and they don’t go and vote because they say it’s hopeless.” Five down, four down, three down means, gee, he has a chance. 17 down means, darling, let’s go to dinner, let’s have a wonderful dinner. And then we’ll come home and watch the President lose, but we’re not going to lose. We’re going to win. We’re going to win. True. True story.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Isn’t that some story? Isn’t that sad? And he knows the people. He said, “No, this is the way they do it.” And then they came with another state where I was 10 down that I’m going to actually win the state. It’s a terrible thing. We have tremendous dishonesty in polling, but not only polling. I mean, the stories. And now there’s something that happened. We call it freedom of the press, right? This is the opposite of freedom of the press, because they now suppress.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: It’s now suppression of the press, because now they have stories and they don’t want to have … you cannot get a story out on Biden criminality. We have the laptop from hell. We have the worst things anyone’s ever seen, and they just won’t write about it. And that includes big tech. So you know what I’m doing? Here’s who I’m facing, a corrupt Democrat party that spied on my campaign and we caught them. They spied on the campaign.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Audience
transcription: Lock them up. Lock him up. Lock him up. Lock him up. Lock him up. Lock him up. Lock him up. Lock him up. Lock him up.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Thank you. See, I never do anything to encourage it. Because they say, “He led the chant. Lock him up, lock him up. He led the chant against crooked Hillary.” All she did was get rid of 33,000 emails once she got a subpoena from Congress. She deleted them. She acid washed them, and then she took a hammer to a telephones and she beat the hell out of the phone. I’ve gotten rid of a lot of phones, I’ve never hit them with a hammer. Has anybody hit the phone with a hammer? I don’t know. Well, we’ll have to tell that to Ron Johnson. We can put that. That is a strange event, Ron. I bet you never hit your phone with a hammer. No, it’s called you throw it out, right? You throw out your phone, you start all over again.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: No, we’ve got a corrupt bunch of people, but think of it. I’m all up here alone. Think of this. I have the Democrats impeach me for making a phone call. No, I make a phone call to a man I never met. The new President of Ukraine. “Congratulations, congratulations.” It was a perfect phone call. Everybody said it. 297 to nothing in the house, the Republicans voted, right? It’s like this perfect phone call, congratulate> Everyone said to me, “Please call him, he just won.” You know I’m busy, right? I say, “Okay, I’ll call him.” Get the president. Nice guy. “Congratulations, ba, ba, ba. By the way, if you see any crime,” because it we’re supposed to … we have a crime because it’s a lot of corruption there, “Please report it to the Attorney General of the United States.” Oh, we should impeach him.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: I got impeached over a perfect phone call, but they didn’t know we had the call essentially recorded. Thank goodness we had, because they were making up stories, right? They died when they heard we had it transcribed by very professional people. They died because it had already been way down the track by the time they found that out, I had to do that. We called up, we said, “Do you mind if we put your phone call on public record?” They said, “Why would that be? It was just a congratulatory call.” I said, “Well, you’ll find out.” These are bad people.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: So here’s where we have. We have the Democrats. Now we have big tech. Now we also have the rhinos. Now the rhinos in many ways are worse than all of them. And most of the rhinos I beat because they were all representing one of the 17, because we had 18 running, but they were … who most of whom I get along with. Some of them I don’t like, I can tell you the good ones and the bad ones, but I beat all of these guys. And they ended up being rhinos and bad people. And here we are. And we’re President. I think we’re going to have something that’s even better than what we did four years ago. I really believe that. I really believe it. Because you don’t have crowds like this and be on the losing side. You leave here, he said, “Gee, that doesn’t sound like a second place. You can’t even see the end of the crowd. That doesn’t look like a second place finisher.” So when you hear about suppression, you have some very nice people up there, about two of them. But when you hear that, that’s right, I know every one of them there, some of them are great, actually, but we’re going to have a big victory.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: And this election is the most important election of our lifetime. This is a more important election than the last one, and I never thought I’d say it because they have gone so far radical left that we have to make this final step. And we’re going to be normalizing our country, really normalizing our country.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: And you know what else normalizes it? Success. I’ll tell you, before the plague came in from China, they should have never let it happen. But before the plague came in from China, I was getting calls from people that you would least expect. It was time. We had the best numbers, the best employment, the best everything, the stock market all time high, everything was the best. And they were like, “Let’s talk,” and it was happening. Then we got hit with the plague. Success brings this country together, and we’re going to have success next year. We’re going to have success next year.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: The most successful year Wisconsin ever had was last year. You’re going to have a year. I mean, unless some guy gets in that wants to quadruple your taxes, which he wants to do. He’s the only guy I’ve ever seen, “We will raise your taxes.” All my life I’ve seen politicians say, we’re going to cut your taxes. He’s the only guy ever campaigning on. He’s going to increase your taxes. In 2016, Wisconsin voted to fire this corrupt political establishment. And you elected an outsider as President who is finally putting America first.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: If I don’t sound like a typical politician is because I’m not a politician, if that’s okay. And if I don’t always play by the rules of Washington and the Washington establishment, it’s because I was elected to fight for you. And I fight harder for you than any President at any time in the history of our country.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Audience
transcription: We love you. We love you. We love you. We love you. We love you. We love you. We love you. We love you.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: That’s so nice. Thank you. That’s a chant that has never been heard politically. Nobody’s ever … even these people, they have … there’s never been a time. We like Ronald Reagan. We like people, but they’ve never had that chant, so it’s an honor. Don’t keep it going too long, because I’ll start to cry. I’ll get a little. And we can’t tell President Xi of China that the President was crying because they said they loved him. Right?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: And the fake news would report it, “President Trump broke down in tears, as they shouted,” somehow it doesn’t work for us. Right? We can’t do that. Right. Look at him. He goes, “No way, you can’t do it.” No, we appreciate it. It is. It’s a chant that nobody’s ever heard before. It started happening like six weeks ago. And I said, “Man, that’s very unusual,” but it’s a beautiful chant and I appreciate it.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: I’m not just running against sleepy Joe Biden. I’m running against the left wing media, the big tech giants and the Washington swamp, and it’s deep and vicious. And they can’t believe what’s happening. They can’t believe it. They would have taken most people out. Almost anybody would have been taken out.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: And I have been helped a lot by that man right there named Ron Johnson. I have. It’s true. He’s a tough guy and he’s a smart guy. And I knew it earlier than anybody else. I knew it. I had a meeting with Ron Johnson and we were going to have a very complex tax. Most people had no idea what we were even talking about. He understood it so good. I mean, so he really understood it. So I knew a long time ago, what you had. Don’t lose him. Don’t ever lose him.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: You need to show up in record numbers and deliver a blistering defeat to these corrupt forces. And they are corrupt as hell. They’re trying to take over our country, and we caught them. They’re coming for your guns. They’re coming for your jobs, and they’re coming for your freedom. Think about it. Your vote will stop them on November 3rd, get out there. You got to vote. It’s the most important issue. One of the most truly important issues.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: You don’t like to even mention it, but as law and order. And I mentioned that to Biden during one of the debates, I said, “Hey, Joe, say the words law and order, can you do it?” He wouldn’t do it because he didn’t want to lose the radical left. He didn’t want to lose them. Joe Biden and his party have spent the entire year inciting violence and hatred against our police officers. He refuses to say, you got to stop it. You cannot run through Portland to destroy the city.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: I mean, it’s been going on. We could stop it in 30 minutes. In Seattle, I said, “I don’t care. We waited and waited. The Governor never called. We waited. I said, “You got to go in.” They took over a part of the city. I mean, this is even … to even talk about this, who would think of this? Seattle. And we were going in and we told them, “We’re coming in the morning,” and you know what they did? That evening they raised their hand and they left. That was the end of it. And a lot of people are paying a big price, by the way, but they raised their hands and they left.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Or the statues. We signed a law, you knock down statutes … They were knocking down statues all over the country. You knock down statues, you go to jail for 10 years. It’s an old law. It’s amazing how we haven’t seen too much trouble with statutes. There were groups that formed. They wanted to do it. They wanted, and then they said, “Let’s get the hell out of here.” 10 years, 10 years. It says 10 years in prison, old law that we reenacted. You could never get that passed today with this crazy group, Nancy Pelosi and crying Chuck Schumer.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Crying Chuck Schumer and Nancy would never pass anything like that. They’d say, “No, you’re allowed to rip down anything you want.” We have a DC mayor that set up a commission, to talk about all of the things, cancel culture let’s talk about. They don’t like the Washington monument. They want it renamed or taken down. This was their recommendation. But don’t worry about it. We’re not doing, I promise you. They don’t like the Thomas Jefferson Memorial because they don’t like it. They don’t even know why. Tell me why. And they don’t like even the Lincoln Memorial, right? They don’t like the Lincoln.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: So they wanted recommendations to change the name or take them down. And I said, “I think this commission should be immediately disbanded because it’s not going anywhere.” But they are. I mean, this is a fact. Take down the Washington monument. These people are stone cold crazy. You have to go out and you have to vote.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Biden stands with the rioters and looters, and Biden wouldn’t say anything about the report. They asked him about the report, he didn’t want to comment. “I have no comment.” Do you want to take down the Washington monument? “I have no comment on that.” Oy yoy yoy, he has no clue. He never had much of a clue. Now we know he …
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: I stand with the heroes of law enforcement. These are great people. We have to help them. If Biden wins, the rioters in the streets, they’ll be running your Federal government. There’ll be running your government. No city, no family and no community will be safe. The Biden-Harris. How about Harris? Kamala. Kamala. And you have to say her name right or she gets very upset, right? Even though she doesn’t say it right.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: But the Biden-Harris plan would end cash bail releasing 400,000 dangerous criminals immediately onto your streets, murderers and rapists. What’s going on is crazy. When the violent mob came to a place known as Kenosha, did you ever hear of Kenosha? Because I did. Remember what I did? If I didn’t activate immediately, Kenosha would not be there any longer. They were going to take it down. Biden opposed sending in the National Guard and I insisted on it. And I frankly wish the Governor asked me sooner, but at least he asked me, but we came in and that was over at about another 15 minutes, right? That didn’t take long. That didn’t take long. And we saved Kenosha. So you still have Kenosha.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: They knocked down and they burned a couple of buildings down. I went, I met with the people, and really good people. What was there 100 years? It was a photography store, was 100 years. They burned down the store, but it’s going to get rebuilt. But we stopped it. That whole area would have been burned to the ground. So we came in and it was so easy too. It’s easy, but you sometimes have to meet force with force. You can’t just stand back, sit back and watch it take place like they did in Minneapolis. Then we went in and it took place very quickly.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Usually if it takes like more than a half an hour to wipe the whole thing out, I say, you’re not doing a very good job. Biden’s running mate, the most liberal Senator in America, even urged their supporters to donate to a fund that bailed out the rioters, took them right out of jail, including a cop killer or an attempted cop killer.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Biden wants to lock down your homes. He’s ready to lock it down. I mean, you guys are already in a lock down, so you might not notice it as much. Hey, Governor, you got to open up your state here. You got to open it up. You’ve got to open up your state. Got to open it up.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: It’s sad. It’s sad, you got to go back. You understand? You’re going to socially distance. You’re going to do all the things you want to do. But I mean, we’re having these outdoor rallies. They say outdoor. Outdoor, normally would go into an arena. I actually like this stuff better. Although sometimes it’s snowing and sleet. I loved that last stop, but it was, the rain was pouring like sideways. It was going, “Sss,” that stuff. That’s when you say, I love the indoor arenas, but I like these. With a day like this it’s so beautiful. It’s great. Is there any place better to be that a Trump rally? No, seriously. It’s great.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: But this election is a choice between a Trump super boom or a Biden depression. That’s what it is. And it’s also between opening up and keeping it closed. You see what’s happening in Europe? They’re trying it again. They’re going to close up. They closed up and they destroyed their economy. Our economy is so much better, so much stronger. Went down so much less. And now it’s come up faster than any country in the world. But ours is between a safe vaccine, which is coming very shortly, it’s momentarily, or a devastating lockdown. That’s what Biden wants to do because he has no choice.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: He will not call the shots. He will not call the shots, and everybody knows it. Thanks to our historic campaign to slash red tape and mobilize industry, we will deliver a safe vaccine to the American people in literally over the next few weeks we think, over the next few weeks. There was a lot of pressure. There was a lot of pressure on everybody, including on the FDA, not to let this happen before the election.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: So let me tell you, if Biden was in charge of this vaccine, just like the swine flu. He was in charge of H1N1, right? Which he can never get right. He can’t remember it. It’s always messed up. Sometime he does N1H1. And I say, “No.” But it’s the swine flu. I said, “Just call it the swine flu. It’s easier.” Right? It’s the same thing. Call it the swine flu. That was a catastrophe. And his own Chief of Staff said it was the dumbest run thing they’ve ever done. And the lethality is much less than what this was and is, was, and sort of was because we have therapeutics now that are incredible. In fact, here I am. I’m here, right?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: They gave me a shot, Regeneron it’s called, and now there’s Eli Lilly now have the antibody stuff. And I’d like to say it had no impact, but I wasn’t feeling good. I like to say, because of my physical power, my strength, my young age. I made the case. I made the case. CNN got very angry. I said, “I’m not concerned.” No, I said, “When I got better, I got better quick.”
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Audience
transcription: Superman. Superman. Superman. Superman. Superman.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: No, CNN got very angry. Fake news. CNN is totally fake. I said, “No, I beat it because I’m in perfect physical shape,” and I’m a very young …
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: I beat it because I’m in perfect physical shape, and I’m a very young person. Well, our First Lady got it. She got better. Barron got it. He got better so fast, we didn’t even know. We said, the doctor said, “Sir, Barron has tested positive.” I said, “For what?” He’s very young and very tall. He’s seriously tall. He’s a good kid, but he’s a strong kid, but he’s a kid and the immune systems, so they said, Dr. Shaw, and he’s great. He’s White House physician. He said, “Barron tested positive.” I said, “For what?” He said, “For COVID.” There’s like 30 different names. I happened to call it the China plague or the China virus, because it’s more accurate. Right?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: About 14 minutes later, I said, “How’s Barron doing? “Well, he’s recovered, fully.” I said, “Barron, were you feeling bad?” “I didn’t know anything, Dad. What was wrong, Dad?” By the way, speaking to that, get back to school. Get back to school. Okay? Get back to school, right? Look, Ron [inaudible 00:37:13] agrees. Seniors be the first in line to get it, and we will, we’re making it available free, because it’s not your fault that this thing happened. The vaccine, by the way, with or without the vaccine, we’re rounding the turn, but the vaccine makes it go faster. The vaccines are going to be out very soon. Very, very soon. Our vaccine will eradicate the virus and the pandemic, quickly restore normal life. I just want normal life. You do too.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: All we want is normal life. I’m looking up to the sky. A friend of mine said, “You’re the most famous man in the world.” I said, “No, I’m not. No, I’m not.” “No,” he said, “No, who’s more famous than you. You are the most famous man in the world. What are you talking about? Who’s more famous?” I said, “Jesus Christ.” I don’t want to take any chances. I looked up and I said, “It’s not even close.” All right. But, next year will be the greatest economic year in the history of our country. Joe Biden’s plan will delay the vaccine, postpone therapies, crash the economy and lock down the entire country. He doesn’t mind locking down the country. The country could not stand it. You know, we locked it down shortly. We did it. We figured it out. We protect our elderly people, et cetera, but he thinks it’s fine.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: He loves that whole deal. I’ll tell you. All he talks about is COVID. He gets up today. He’s talking COVID, COVID, COVID, COVID, COVID, COVID, COVID. The truth is, we have done an incredible job with the ventilators, the vaccines, the therapeutics, but all he does, because he’s got nothing else he can talk about, because no administration in the history of our country has done what we’ve done. I say it all the time. In the first three and a half years, what we’ve done with tax cuts and regulation cuts and rebuilding our military, which was totally depleted and a disaster. What we’ve done with our military, and so many other things, you know them all. Nobody’s done, and they never even questioned me.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: The fake news with all the cameras, it’s never like where they come, “Oh, you shouldn’t have said that.” Nobody’s done … You think of it, Space Force. We could name, right, we could name so many different things. Under the Biden lockdown, countless Americans will die from suicide, drug overdoses, deferred medical care, and you’ll have no school, no graduations, no weddings, no Thanksgiving, no Christmas, no 4th of July, no future. Other than that, he’s doing a fantastic job. Biden wants to keep everyone locked up, even young Americans who are extremely low risk, like we talked about. He wants to steal the dreams and the future of our young people. One thing we’ve learned, the the computers are great and the laptops, everything’s great.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: For telehealth, it’s been great, where people can stay in, and that’s really been, I think it’s up like 7000% or something. It’s a great thing. But you know, for school learning, it’s terrible. It doesn’t work. It can’t compare to a class or a campus. They’re trying so hard to say, “Oh gee, this is wonderful.” It doesn’t compare. It’s well-documented. You’re taking a large percentage of a young life out of play. It’s a terrible thing you’re doing to young kids. It’s a terrible thing that’s happening with the parents too, because the kid’s at school and the parents are working now. The parents don’t know what to do. Many of their jobs are gone, anyway. Now, you got to open up your state. You got to do it fast. You got to do it fast.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Thanks to our relentless efforts, only 3% of the emergency room visits nationwide are related to the virus. Think of that. 3%, because you know what it is? They only talk about cases. The reason we have so many cases, because we test. If I tested half, they said, “Test, test, test.” We test more than any country in the world, by far. We have the best tests. These are things that we never even had six months ago. Now, if I said, “Let’s cut the testing down in half, you’d have half. Everyone would say, “Oh, the cases are way down.” Right? But, you know what? It’s good because we know if there’s a problem, et cetera, et cetera. We know if there’s a hotspot. But that’s exactly what it is. I mean, but what we do and what we’ve done so well, other therapies, and if you think of it, the fatality rate is down 85% and more now. Think of that.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: But, they talk about cases because when you hear 3% of the emergency rooms are devoted … It’s supposed to be 100%, and the hospitals are going to close. They don’t know what’s going on. It’s been amazing what we’ve been able to do, but you don’t hear them talking about death. You hear them talking about, because as a percentage, what we’ve done compared to other countries is incredible. Now, especially with the explosion that you see taking place over in Europe. We’ve done a great job, and I’ll tell you what, our Vice President has been fantastic. You compare Vice-Presidents and if you don’t mind, I’ll take the one we have. Okay?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: You talk about a victory at a debate. That was one of the greatest victories at a debate I’ve ever seen. That one wasn’t even close. Our excess mortality rate is 42% lower than Europe’s. Think of that. Where cases are now surging, despite very powerful lockdowns that they’ve been put. In. They’ve had very powerful lockdowns. But don’t take my word for it. I want to just show you something on a screen. Okay? Very special people get this. We have a video on our fight against the China virus and a couple of other quick things. Again, we only do this for extremely important states, ans people. And Go ahead
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 1
transcription: The fact is, every time I’ve called the president, he’s quickly gotten on the line. When we asked to get support for that mercy ship in Southern California, he was able to direct that in real time.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 2
transcription: What the federal government did working with states, was a phenomenal accomplishment.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 3
transcription: We got 2000 of these field medical sites that are up, almost all operational now, in the state because of his support, and those are the facts.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 4
transcription: His team has been on it. I know a team when they’re on it. I know a team when they’re not on it. His team is on it. They’ve been responsive, late at night, early in the morning.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 3
transcription: We are working very well with FEMA Region 2, and with the Army Corps of Engineers, building four field hospitals. That was the decision the president himself took, and I’m grateful for it.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 4
transcription: These were just extraordinary efforts and acts of mobilization and the federal government stepped up. We needed help and they were there.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 5
transcription: He said everything that I could have hoped for. We had a very long conversation and every single thing he said, they followed through on.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 6
transcription: We’ve got to have double the number of ventilators that we requested for that area of the state. In fact, we got them in frankly, short order.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 4
transcription: Have we lost anyone because we didn’t have a bed or we didn’t have a ventilator? Well, we didn’t have healthcare staff? No.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 7
transcription: The president was extending support for new swabs. A conversation, commitment, a promise made, promise kept.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 8
transcription: My problem is, I voted for NAFTA. I’m supporting NAFTA because I think it is the positive thing to do. I do not pretend to be an expert on international trade matters.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 9
transcription: Trade agreements, like NAFTA and permanent normal trade relations with China, which forced American workers to compete against people who making pennies an hour, has resulted in the loss of 160,000 jobs.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 10
transcription: The president is absolutely right, when he says that China has been cheating for 25 years and that Bill Clinton didn’t didn’t do enough about it. George W. Bush didn’t do enough about it. Barack Obama didn’t do enough about it.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 11
transcription: Rising China is an incredibly positive development for not only China, but the United States and the rest of the world. Rising China is positive, positive development. It is in our self-interest that China continue to prosper. We want to see China rise.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 12
transcription: China’s a great nation, and we should hope for the continued expansion.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 13
transcription: China is not our enemy.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 14
transcription: We talk about China as our competitor. We should be helping.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 15
transcription: The idea that China is going to eat our lunch is bizarre.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 16
transcription: The idea that they are the competition. They’re not bad folks, folks. China’s not a problem.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 17
transcription: Allowing China into the World Trade Organization, which he supported, extending Most Favored Nation Status to China, which he supported. Those steps allowed China to take advantage of the United States by using our own open trade deals against us.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 18
transcription: Do you think, in retrospect, that you were naive about China?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Joe Biden
transcription: No.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 18
transcription: But, doesn’t he deserve some credit for that? It’s better. The USMCA is better than NAFTA.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Joe Biden
transcription: It is better than NAFTA.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 19
transcription: Now, to be fair, maybe Biden’s not telling us, because he’s forgotten his own plants. Watch Biden’s staff quickly swoop in to shuffle him along. During a quickie escape, the basement trip to Pennsylvania.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 20
transcription: Here’s the deal. One of the things that that is important, is that, keep in mind, although they’re going to vote on [inaudible 00:47:37].
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 19
transcription: That was terrifying.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Joe Biden
transcription: What kind of country are going to be? Four more years of George, George …we’re going to find ourselves in a position where if Trump gets elected, we’re going to be in a different world.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: You know, I like that, because I save a lot of words. You can never duplicate what you see up there, but you see the governors. Then, they’ll say, although some of them have been actually very good, but we’ve done a great job and you see it there. That’s what their real feeling is. But when they get up to a mic, “Well, I don’t know if he’s done that good.” Now, we’ve done a great job. If you want a vaccine to kill the virus, a job to support your family, and freedom to live your life to the fullest, you have to vote republican. It’s so important. You have to vote Republican. We’re joined today with some really great people and a man that’s right at the top of that list for me, is Senator Ron Johnson. Thank you, Ron. I’m telling you, you’re lucky to have him. He’s a fantastic man. He’s done an incredible job and he’s got a lot of courage too. In Washington, he’s respected by everybody. Also, Congressman Glenn Grothman. Glenn? There’s Glenn. Thank you, Glenn. Mike Gallagher. Thanks, Mike. Great job. Great guys. Somebody that’s done a really good job for us, GOP chairman, Andrew Hitt. Thank you. Thank you, Andrew. How are we doing Andrew?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Andrew Hitt
transcription: Doing great, Sir.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: All right. Because we don’t, we’re not going to fire you so damn … You’ll be out of here, Andrew. No, I think we’re doing great. Yeah, I think we’re doing great. I also want to thank a legendary champion and a Green Bay Packer, personified Hall of Famer, Brett Farve, for his endorsement. I got, he’s a tough guy. He’s great. But, ,two days ago I saw that he endorsed me and I just want to thank him. He’s a hell of a champion. He’s a great champion. I look at some of his records. You don’t even realize it, but when you look at passing yards and touchdowns, and one thing about him, tough as hell and great and really talented. I want to thank Brett Farve. Thank you very much
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: For decades, our politicians spent trillions of dollars rebuilding foreign nations. Now we are rebuilding, if it’s okay with you, our nation. I ended the NAFTA nightmare and replaced it with a brand new UMSCA. Wisconsin dairy farmers were decimated under the Obama and Biden plan. Just think about it. I only ran because of them. I said that during the debate. I said, “Joe, never thought of this, I ran because of you people, because you did such a bad job.” He had no response to that. With the USMCA, are dairy exports to Canada are expected to surge by more than 100%. Okay? Just went into effect and we’re not going to be losing our companies to Mexico and Canada. We’re not going to have our companies close up and get rid of everybody, fire everybody. And move and do the same product in Mexico.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: You saw that. It’s probably the number one reason I ran. I couldn’t stand watching it and it’s going to be, now, they’re going to pay a tremendous economic price if they do that. Joe Biden is a corrupt politician. They took millions of dollars from the Chinese Communist Party, while Vice President Biden shipped your jobs to China. How the hell can he negotiate with China with the money they take. The news, they don’t want to cover it. The fake media, the lame stream media and the companies, right? These wonderful companies that obviously don’t love our country. It’s suppression. They don’t want to cover it. If Biden wins, China wins. His son walks in and takes out one and a half billion dollars to manage millions of dollars a year. They walk in.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: Speaker 21
transcription: Where’s Hunter?
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Where’s Hunter? He wants to know, where’s Hunter? We haven’t found him. He’s still looking for his laptop from hell. That’s where he is. “Where’s my laptop?” “Hunter, you left it at a repair shop. You’d never picked it up.” You know what they go? “Russia did it. Russia, Russia, Russia, Ron it’s Russia. I know it’s Russia.” I saw Adam Schiff, watermelon head, like this. “I believe that Russia caused his problem. Russia.” Yeah. Yeah. Here we go. Russia, Russia, Russia. We have a great head of DNI. He said, “No, it had nothing to do with Russia.” Put out a very strong statement, nothing to do. If it does, we let it know. We let Russia know. But this is pure, disgusting, evil stuff that goes on. Your tech companies don’t want to put it on you. Even the New York Post, which had real courage by the way, and they endorsed me two days ago. That’s [inaudible 00:52:59] But, they had real courage. They took down the New York Post site. Can you believe it? The New York Post, the oldest newspaper in the country, fourth largest of the country. They took down the site. Now, we got to get to the bottom of it. We will, with guys like Kim, we will. When we win, Wisconsin wins. When we win, America wins, and that’s what’s happening. Under my leadership, we achieved the most secure border in US history. We have now built over 400 miles of wall. We’ll soon be finished. They don’t talk about the wall anymore. They don’t tell you. It used to kill me. I’d to go through with, and fight them and we’d close up and we’d do all sorts of things. They would go after me. Once the wall started, once they saw we had all that money lined up to get it done. The impact it’s had is incredible. It’s not completed yet, but it will be very soon. I built it exactly as Border Patrol and ICE wanted it. Exactly. I said, “What about concrete-”
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: … And ICE wanted it exactly. I said, “What about concrete plank?” They said, “Sir, that’s no good. Have to see through.” “Well, how about this? And how about that?” I know it all. That’s what I like. They said, “Sir, we want steel. We, then, want concrete inside the steel, and then, we’d like rebar.” I said, “Can you think of a more expensive way, maybe?”
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: But we gave it. And then, we want on top an anti-climb, you know the thing on top? I said, “Why are we doing that? That’s very expensive. The piece of steel on top is four feet deep.” They said, “Sir, that’s called anti-climb. It’s harder to climb.” I gave them everything. Now, they have no excuse. I don’t want to have any excuses. And our numbers on the border are phenomenal, the best we’ve ever had. Joe Biden has pledged to open borders, mass amnesty, nationwide catch-and-release. You know what that is? That’s when you catch a criminal, murderer, rapist, you let the criminal go. We argued about this during the debate. He said, “They all come back for a trial.” No, they don’t come back, Joe. Only the ones, I said, with very low IQs, come back. You have a trial in two-and-a-half years for murder, you have to come back.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: We release them, and I ended it. It’s all ended. Okay. You think that was easy? It’s not easy doing this stuff. It looks easy, but it’s not. Sanctuary cities from coast to coast. They want to have sanctuary cities all over the place, and free healthcare for illegal aliens, which will bankrupt your Medicare and your social security. You will not have social security if you do that or Medicare. We all have a big heart. I do. I want to take care of everybody. The problem is you have millions of people pouring in from all over the world if you do this. As your president, I will protect your borders, I will protect your families, and I will always protect your Medicare and your social security. And I’ve always said it.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Biden and Bernie Sanders, crazy Bernie, one of the greatest losers of all time, this guy. No, but I meant that in a nice way. He lost, and he went back to the Senate and voted radical left, that he lost again. Elizabeth Pocahontas Warren, all she had to do is get out a couple of days early. He would have won every one of those days, but she decided not to do that. I don’t think she likes Bernie, okay? But Biden will increase refugees. This was agreed with Bernie and the group and AOC plus three, right? Highly educated person on the environment AOC. Have you ever taken a class on the environment? I don’t think so. Increase refugees by 700% from terror hotspots. So, think of that, as 700… This was agreed to. I don’t think Bernie was that bad. I think, actually, Bernie went further left after they made the deal. And I’m keeping radical Islamic terrorists the hell out of our country. Okay? If it’s okay with you.
headlin: Donald Trump Rally Speech Transcript Green Bay, Wisconsin October 30

speaker: President Donald Trump
transcription: Look at what’s gone on in France over the four days, what’s happened in France. We invested $2.5 trillion in the US military, including nearly $6 billion to save the historic shipyard, Marinette Marine, And even more money for combat vehicle manufacturing in Oshkosh. Marinette’s doing a great job. I went to Marinette four or five months ago, looked at what they were doing. We gave the contract to them, which costs me a lot of states, but that’s okay. But we gave that to Marinette. They do a great job. They do a great job. They were ready to close. A $6 billion contract, and it’s going to be extended. They make the most beautiful ship. You have to say, it looks like a super yacht except it’s got weapons all over it. And I would say, “Paint it gleaming white and call it a yacht.
